@startuml stm_primary
title <<stm>> CRenderContext Primary State Machine
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<browse>> #e3f2fd
    BorderColor<<browse>> #1565c0
    FontColor<<browse>> #0d47a1
    BackgroundColor<<terminal>> #e8f5e9
    BorderColor<<terminal>> #2e7d32
}
skinparam shadowing false
top to bottom direction

state "pre_construct" as Pre <<browse>>
state "active" as Active <<browse>>
state "primitive_open" as PrimOpen <<browse>>
state "destroyed" as Dead <<terminal>>

Pre -down-> Active : construct(pd3dDev)
Active --> PrimOpen : begin(lines/triangles/quads/...)
PrimOpen --> PrimOpen : vertex(_) / normal(_)
PrimOpen --> Active : end
Active --> Active : set_color/set_alpha\nsetup_lines/setup_*\nload/mult_matrix\ntranslate/rotate\npush/pop_matrix\nbind(Tex)/unbind\ncreate_vertex_buffer [D3D8]\ntriangles_from_surface(Mesh)
Active -down-> Dead : destruct
PrimOpen -down-> Dead : destruct [unbalanced; bug]

note right of Active
    HALF-MIGRATED: holds
    LPDIRECT3DDEVICE8 but
    every method except
    create_vertex_buffer
    uses OpenGL.
end note
@enduml
